{"tid":2100041,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【開庭第一日】 Johnny Deep庭上承認吸毒並為未成年女兒提供毒品","createTime":"2020-07-08T17:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T18:19:30.000Z","uid":280250,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f747d861539af30785a459afb40c490fda3d58da","tid":2100041,"uid":280250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:36:33.000Z","msg":"我上Twitter 睇 depp承認咗吸毒同埋提供毒品比佢個囡(當時13歲而且加州大麻18年先合法化)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHcyXKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHcyXKD.jpg&h=f0a50725&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYU16CZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYU16CZ.jpg&h=889c6ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女方舉證嘅圖，depp食cocaine<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tcryir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tcryir.jpg&h=5a17a2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibdVrDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FibdVrDr.jpg&h=3d727af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有depp同paul bettany&ldquo;講笑&rdquo;話要燒死amber並且奸焦屍，確認amber死咗並且再淹了她來確認佢不是女巫，還威脅amber要將佢隻狗放入微波爐<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vF6ctSJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvF6ctSJ.jpg&h=6479e7f4&s={SIZE}\" />paul：我們給amber買一個飛機杯（直譯係玩具陰部，應該就係咁解），拍張你給它剃毛的照片，然後我們就可以建個叫Amber heard的陰部的網站，賺他媽的一大筆錢<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1CZTka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1CZTka.jpg&h=80e2cae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時ah澄清喺床度屙屎嗰個係佢隻狗，隻狗一直都腸胃唔舒服，仲要係因為食咗depp 啲大麻先喺床度屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(呢個大家自行定奪)<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YN5kCOj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYN5kCOj.jpg&h=517a8170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而去旁聽庭審嘅記者話depp承認婚姻期間同另一個女人有relationship overlap<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXq8MG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXq8MG1.jpg&h=a10c7ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上咁多都係Twitter 上面搵到，有興趣可以自己去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申我唔係邊個嘅fans，只不過睇返之前幾個po大家都好似Miss咗好多野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />depp不利嘅消息冇乜，女方就大把，事情有兩面睇，其實今日係佢地開庭第一日，仲有兩個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇嚟有好多花生食，<span class=\"small\">雖然我個人偏向呢兩個都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7647de282267943e401e49b91af93d8c780e394f","tid":2100041,"uid":286155,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"個女人應該係奸嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7915410a448c55e96a4f58de67cf279a3f8dc29","tid":2100041,"uid":280250,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"7647de282267943e401e49b91af93d8c780e394f","tid":2100041,"uid":286155,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"個女人應該係奸嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:46:23.000Z","msg":"講真我覺得兩條友都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗咬狗骨"},{"pid":"104d01d73a39e058262ba09e100e815acde71ab2","tid":2100041,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:11:06.000Z","msg":"唔錯"},{"pid":"aa911279e404b6a1b00b9ddf0d332fc09fef3e71","tid":2100041,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:59:29.000Z","msg":"好撚精彩<br />\n第時去到英國啲鬼妹係咪都係咁喪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚驚"},{"pid":"3134674f351d6e92e555a6108f6794612f9b10a3","tid":2100041,"uid":280250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa911279e404b6a1b00b9ddf0d332fc09fef3e71","tid":2100041,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"cited